\c 19
\s Ezulwini kukhona injabulo ngomtshado weWundlu
\p
\v 1 Emva kwalezizinto ngasengisizwa ilizwi elikhulu elexuku elikhulu ezulwini\x + 11.15.\x*, lisithi: \w Haleluya\w**\x + 19.3,4,6.\x*! Usindiso\x + 7.10.\x* lobukhosi\x + 4.9.\x* lodumo\x + 4.9.\x* lamandla kungokweNkosi uNkulunkulu wethu\x + 12.10. Hlab. 62.11.\x*;
\v 2 ngoba izigwebo zakhe ziqotho zilungile\x + 16.7.\x*; ngoba usilahlile\x + 6.10.\x* isifebe esikhulu\x + 17.1.\x*, esonakalise umhlaba ngobufebe baso, usephindisele igazi lenceku zakhe esandleni saso\x + 6.10.\x*\x + Dute. 32.43. 2 Kho. 9.7.\x*.
\v 3 Basebesithi ngokwesibili: Haleluya\x + 19.3,4,6.\x*! Lentuthu yaso ithunqa kuze kube nini lanini\x + 14.11. 18.9,18.\x*.
\v 4 Labadala abangamatshumi amabili lane lezidalwa ezine eziphilayo zawela phansi zakhonza uNkulunkulu\x + 5.8,14. 4.4.\x* ohlezi esihlalweni sobukhosi zisithi: Ameni\x + 5.14.\x*! Haleluya\x + 19.3,4,6.\x*!
\v 5 Ilizwi laseliphuma livela esihlalweni sobukhosi, lisithi: Mdumiseni uNkulunkulu wethu\x + Luka 2.13,20.\x*, lina lonke zinceku zakhe\x + Hlab. 134.1; 135.1.\x*, labamesabayo\x + 11.18.\x*, labancinyane, labakhulu\x + 11.18.\x*\x + 19.18. Seb. 26.22.\x*.
\v 6 Ngasengisizwa kungathi yilizwi lexuku elikhulu\x + Dan. 10.6. Hez. 1.24.\x*, njalo kungathi ngumdumo wamanzi amanengi\x + 1.15.\x*, njalo kungathi ngumsindo wemidumo elamandla\x + 6.1.\x*, kusithi: Haleluya!\x + 19.3,4,6.\x* Ngoba iNkosi uNkulunkulu\x + 11.15.\x* uSomandla uyabusa\x + 19.15. 2 Kor. 6.18.\x*.
\v 7 Asithokoze sithabe kakhulu, besesisipha udumo kuye\x + 11.13.\x*; ngoba umtshado weWundlu usufikile\x + 19.9. Mat. 22.2; 25.1.\x*, lomkalo usezilungisele\x + Isa. 54.5. 2 Kor. 11.2. Isam. 21.2,9; 22.17.\x*.
\v 8 Kwasekuphiwa kuye\x + Hlab. 45.14,15. Hez. 16.10.\x* ukuthi embathe\x + 3.5,18.\x* ilembu elicolekileyo kakhulu\x + 19.14. 18.12.\x* elihlanzekileyo lelikhazimulayo\x + 15.6. 19.14.\x*; ngoba ilembu elicolekileyo kakhulu\x + Jobe 29.14.\x* liyikulunga kwabangcwele\x + Roma 5.16,18. 1 Kor. 1.30.\x*.
