\v 9 Yasisithi kimi: Bhala \add uthi\x + 14.13.\x*\add*: Babusisiwe labo ababizelwe ekudleni kwantambama komtshado weWundlu\x + Luka 14.15. Isam. 19.7.\x*. Yasisithi kimi: La ngamazwi aqotho kaNkulunkulu\x + 21.5; 22.6.\x*.
\v 10 Ngasengiwela phansi enyaweni zayo ukuyikhonza\x + 22.8.\x*; yasisithi kimi: Qaphela unga\add kwenzi\x + 22.9. Seb. 10.26.\x*\add*; ngiyinceku kanye lawe labazalwane bakho abalobufakazi bukaJesu\x + 12.17.\x*; khonza uNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 4.10.\x*; ngoba ubufakazi bukaJesu\x + 1.2.\x* bungumoya wesiprofetho\x + 11.3.\x*.
\s UKristu ulwa lesilo asinqobe
\p
\v 11 Ngasengibona izulu livuliwe\x + Seb. 10.11. Hez. 1.1. Isam. 11.19; 15.5.\x*, khangela-ke ibhiza elimhlophe\x + 6.2. 19.19,21.\x*, loligadileyo\x + 6.2. 19.19,21.\x* ubizwa ngokuthi oThembekileyo\x + 3.14.\x*\x + 1.5.\x* loQotho\x + 3.14.\x*\x + 3.7.\x*, njalo ngokulunga uyahlulela alwe\x + Isa. 11.4.\x*.
\v 12 Lamehlo akhe afanana lelangabi lomlilo\x + 1.14.\x*, lekhanda lakhe\x + 6.2; 14.14.\x* kulemiqhele eminengi\x + 12.3.\x*; njalo ulebizo elilotshiweyo\x + 19.16.\x*, okungelamuntu olaziyo ngaphandle kwakhe\x + 2.17. Zaga 30.4. Mat. 11.27.\x*,
\v 13 wasesembatha isembatho esicwiliswe egazini\x + Isa. 63.2,3.\x*; lebizo lakhe libizwa \add ngokuthi\add*, nguLizwi likaNkulunkulu\x + Joha. 1.1.\x*.
\v 14 Lamabutho ayesezulwini amlandela egade amabhiza amhlophe\x + 14.20.\x*, embethe ilembu elicolekileyo kakhulu\x + 19.8. 3.4.\x* elimhlophe lelihlanzekileyo\x + 19.8. 3.4.\x*.
\v 15 Emlonyeni wakhe kwasekuphuma inkemba ebukhali\x + 19.21. Isa. 11.4. 2 Thes. 2.8. Isam. 1.16.\x*, ukuze atshaye izizwe ngayo; njalo yena uzazibusa ngentonga yensimbi\x + 2.27.\x*; yena-ke uzanyathela isikhamelo sevini sewayini\x + Isa. 63.2,3.\x*\x + 14.19,20.\x* lentukuthelo lolaka\x + 14.10.\x* lukaNkulunkulu uSomandla\x + 19.6.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo esembathweni lethangazini lakhe ulebizo elibhalwe\x + 19.12.\x* \add ukuthi\add*: INKOSI YAMAKHOSI LOMBUSI WABABUSI\x + 17.14.\x*.
