\v 17 Ngasengibona ingilosi eyodwa imi elangeni; yasimemeza ngelizwi elikhulu, isithi enyonini zonke\x + 19.21.\x* eziphaphayo phakathi laphakathi kwezulu\x + 8.13.\x*: Wozani libuthaniswe\x + Jer. 12.9. Hez. 39.17. 1 Sam. 17.44.\x* ekudleni kwantambama\x + Zef. 1.7.\x* kukaNkulunkulu omkhulu\x + Tit. 2.13.\x*,
\v 18 ukuze lidle inyama yamakhosi\x + Hez. 39.18,20. Isam. 17.16.\x*, lenyama yenduna ezinkulu\x + 6.15.\x*, lenyama yabalamandla\x + Hez. 39.18,20. Isam. 17.16.\x*, lenyama yamabhiza leyabagadi bawo\x + Hez. 39.18,20. Isam. 17.16.\x*, lenyama yabo bonke, abakhululekileyo kanye labayizigqili\x + 6.15.\x*, labancinyane labakhulu\x + 19.5.\x*.
