\v 19 Ngasengibona isilo\x + 11.7.\x*, lamakhosi omhlaba lamabutho awo ebuthanele\x + 16.16.\x* ukulwa impi laye\x + 16.14.\x* ogade ibhiza\x + 19.11,14,21.\x*, kanye lebutho lakhe.
